            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "because after set `cterm=underline` the `hl_table[142(String index)].sg_set` set to `SG_CTERM` . then do background change invoke `init_highlight(false,false)` in `did_set_backgroud` cb. \r\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/f0eb3ca9163ad10753fbb75558b900a539f76e0d/src/nvim/highlight_group.c#L706-L708\r\n\r\nnew String ctermfg attr in light will be ignored because `sg_set` has been set to `SG_CTERM` this condition is skip so `ctermfg` no longer update.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/f0eb3ca9163ad10753fbb75558b900a539f76e0d/src/nvim/highlight_group.c#L1225-L1226\r\n\r\ntried make it force into condition `if (!init || !(hl_table[idx].sg_set & SG_CTERM) || !forceit) {` then i get\r\n\r\n`String         xxx cterm=underline ctermfg=2 guifg=NvimDarkGreen` . ",
